      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "> **For Individuals (Beneficiaries):**\n\n\n- The applicant must be a person with disability having at least 40% disability, duly certified by a competent medical authority.\n- The applicant must belong to any category such as locomotor, visual, hearing, mental, or multiple disabilities.\n- The applicant must require support for rehabilitation, medical treatment, education, or livelihood.\n\n> **For Organizations:**\n\n\n- The organization must be a registered voluntary organization/NGO/institution.\n- The organization must have experience in implementing disability welfare programmes.\n- The organization must have adequate infrastructure and trained personnel to provide services.\n- The organization must ensure that services are provided without discrimination.\n\n<br>\n\n",
